78
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:52,680
Language Takeaway.
语言要点。

79
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,680
Language Takeaway.
语言要点。

80
00:02:53,680 --> 00:03:00,280
Okay, well this first one might be the reason for surgery, not necessarily a kind of surgery.
好的，第一个可能是手术的原因，不一定是手术的类型。

81
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,520
If someone is vain.
如果某人很虚荣。

82
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:05,040
Okay, so if a person is vain, this is an adjective.
好的，所以如果一个人很虚荣，这是一个形容词。

83
