I love my face, my eyes.
我爱我的脸，我的眼睛。

88
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:19,440
I look so good.
我看起来太棒了。

89
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:23,400
So a person who is vain thinks very highly of themselves.
所以一个虚荣的人对自己评价很高。

90
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,440
Okay, very good.
好的，很好。

91
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:31,200
And well, this person I think wanted to get surgery as well because she said she had wrinkles.
嗯，我觉得这个人也想做手术，因为她说了她有皱纹。

92
