But if you have sagging skin, that means your skin is no longer tight.
但如果你有松弛的皮肤，那意味着你的皮肤不再紧致。

114
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:20,280
It's kind of loose and it hangs.
有点松垮，挂下来。

115
