年轻几个月。

127
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:50,840
I've heard that they also put them in their lips to make them like fuller, right?
我听说他们也会把肉毒杆菌打在嘴唇上，让嘴唇更丰满，对吧？

128
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:51,920
That's right.
没错。

129
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:56,680
And sometimes you can say that someone's had too much Botox because they can no longer
有时候你能看出某人肉毒杆菌打太多了，因为他们再也

130
00:04:56,680 --> 00:05:01,320
smile or they can't stop smiling.
笑不出来，或者一直笑个不停。

131
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,440
Exactly.
正是。

132
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:06,040
And well, very related to this is also when people get a facelift.
嗯，与此非常相关的是，人们还会做面部拉皮手术。

133
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,040
Okay.
好的。

134
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:08,040
A facelift.
面部拉皮。

135
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:14,880
So basically it's that a doctor, a plastic surgeon will tighten the skin on your face
基本上就是医生，一位整形外科医生，会紧致你脸上的皮肤，

136
