所以是为了消除那些皱纹，对吧？

140
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,560
Or the sagging skin.
或者下垂的皮肤。

141
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,560
Right.
对。

142
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,560
Lift means to pull up.
“拉皮”意思是向上提拉。

143
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,560
Right.
对。

144
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,560
It's the opposite of sag.
这是“下垂”的反义词。

145
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,560
Very good.
非常好。

146
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,560
Alright.
好了。

147
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:36,320
So this dialogue has a lot of rich vocabulary related to surgery.
所以这段对话有很多与手术相关的丰富词汇。

148
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:40,640
So why don't we listen to our dialogue again and we'll be back with the second part of
那我们再听一遍对话，之后我们会回来继续第二部分

149
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:51,120
language takeaway to explain a little bit more.
语言要点讲解，进一步解释。

150
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,120
What are you doing?
你在干什么？

151
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,120
Look at me.
看看我。

152
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,400
I look so old.
我看起来好老。

153
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:56,480
I look as if I were 30.
我看起来像30岁似的。

154
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,480
Come on.
得了吧。

155
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,680
Stop being so vain.
别这么虚荣了。

156
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,000
You look great.
你看起来很棒。

157
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,000
You are beautiful.
你很漂亮。

158
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,640
Yes, I am.
是的，我是。

159
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:04,800
But I think it's time for some plastic surgery.
但我觉得是时候做点整形手术了。

160
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:07,080
I'm tired of these wrinkles and sagging skin.
我厌倦了这些皱纹和下垂的皮肤。

161
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,320
See?
看到了吗？

162
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:11,240
I don't see any wrinkles or sagging skin.
我没看到任何皱纹或下垂的皮肤。

163
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,640
You're 25.
你才25岁。

164
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,640
Stop being ridiculous.
别这么荒谬了。

165
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:19,360
Besides, I think that people who get Botox, have facelifts or tummy tucks look weird.
而且，我觉得那些打肉毒杆菌、做面部拉皮或腹部除皱的人看起来很奇怪。

166
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:21,120
It doesn't look natural.
看起来不自然。

167
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,120
Whatever.
随便吧。

168
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:26,400
I think I'm going to get liposuction and a nose job and some breast implants as well.
我想我要去做抽脂、隆鼻，还有隆胸。

169
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,800
I think you need to get brain surgery.
我觉得你需要做脑部手术。

170
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:32,040
I honestly don't think you need cosmetic surgery.
我真的不认为你需要做美容手术。

171
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,600
You look amazing.
你看起来美极了。

172
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:36,120
I thought you were my friend and would support me on this.
我以为你是我的朋友，会支持我这个决定。

173
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:39,920
I just want to feel better about myself and feel more attractive.
我只是想让自己感觉更好，更有吸引力。

174
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:43,120
You don't need plastic surgery to do that.
你不需要做整形手术来达到那个目的。

175
